ary role in recruiting to alabama the first mercedesbenz automotive assembly plant outside germany mr topazi served as the director of new orleans branch of federal reserve bank of atlanta he serves as a director of whitney bank he served as director of southern power company he serves as director of mast inc and the gulf coast community foundation and on the nature conservancy of mississippi board of trustees he served as an independent director of hancock holding company since january   until april   he served as a director hancock bank since  he served as a director of mississippi power co from january   to august   he is a member of the de toqueville society of united way of america he chairs the infrastructure committee of the governors commission on recovery rebuilding and renewal momentum mississippi and the gulf coast business council he served on the blueprint mississippi steering committee and cochaired the economic development work team mr topazi serves on mississippi economic council board of directors as vice chair of mississippi partnership for economic development and as chairelect of mississippi gulf coast chamber of commerce he holds bachelors degree in electrical engineering from auburn universityread full background corporate headquarters  us highway hattiesburg mississippi united statesphone fax  board members memberships directorwhitney bank gulfport ms education bachelors degree auburn university other affiliations the southern companyhancock holding companysouthern power companymississippi power cogulf power companyauburn universitywhitney bank gulfport msfederal reserve bank of atlanta annual compensation there is no annual compensation data available stocks options there is no stock options data available total compensation there is no total compensation data available request profile update   the information and data displayed in this profile are created and managed by sp global market intelligence a division of sp global bloombergcom does 