iography anthony j topazi is the former executive vice president and chief operating officer of southern company from  to  based in atlanta southern company is one of the largest generators of electricity in the nation serving both regulated markets across the southeast in mississippi alabama florida and georgia and competitive markets across the us he served as president and chief executive officer of mississippi power company from  to september  mr topazi was an advisory director of hancock bank from  to  when he became a board member of hancock holding company mr topazi is a member of our compensation committee  read more anthony j topazi is the former executive vice president and chief operating officer of southern company from  to  based in atlanta southern company is one of the largest generators of electricity in the nation serving both regulated markets across the southeast in mississippi alabama florida and georgia and competitive markets across the us he served as president and chief executive officer of mississippi power company from  to september  mr topazi was an advisory director of hancock bank from  to  when he became a board member of hancock holding company mr topazi is a member of our compensation committee mr topazi served on the board of the federal reserve bank new orleans branch from  until december  additionally mr topazi has held numerous executive leadership positions with gulf coast business economic and service organizations he served as chairman of momentum mississippi a publicprivate partnership formed in  by governor haley barbour to develop the state of mississippis long term economic development strategy he also served as chairman of the gulf coast business council and as chairman of the gulf coast renaissance corporation which focuses on the redevelopment of the coastal communities and housing for the workforce mr topazi has also served as a board member of the mississippi economic council the mississippi partnership for economic development the gulf coast community foundation and the mississippi gulf coast chamber of commerce mr topazi was named a  financial times outstanding director one of five corporate directors to receive the honor nationally mr topazis considerable senior management and economic development experience as well as his significant regulatory experience given his career in a highlyregulated industry and his tenure on the board of the new orleans branch board of the federal reserve make him qualified to serve as a member of our board source hancock holding company on    sign up for equilar atlas and view anthony j topazis full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like anthony j topazi more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in anthony j topazis network and community follow changes in anthony j topazis employment and moneyinmotion connect with anthony j topazi through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example anthony j topazi anthony j topazis connections  sign up now to view anthony j topazis  connections » larry d thompson board member the southern company francis s blake nonexecutive chairman delta air lines inc donald m james board member the southern company j neal purcell former board member synovus financial corp christine l pickering board member hancock holding company william g smith chairman president and chief executive officer capital city bank group inc henry a clark board member the southern company suzanne c thomas chief credit officer hancock holding company david m ratcliffe board member suntrust banks inc thomas a fanning board member vulcan materials company popular profiles sign up now to view more executive profiles » thomas j lynch executive chairman te connectivity ltd john j kita evp and cfo a o smith elon r musk ceo and chairman tesla jan koum board member facebook inc philip l milstein board mem