in   company name  mississippi power co   company website  wwwmississippipowercom   company address   w beach blvd gulfport msunited states   anthony topazi profile  pres ceo  mississippi power co   anthony topazi biography  anthony j topazi became mississippi powers tenth president and chief executive officer on january   previously topazi was executive vice president at southern company generation  energy marketing responsible for southern companys energy trading and wholesale marketing as well as its fuel services and generation planning and development departments he also served as senior vice president of southern power which owns and manages new generation assets dedicated to the wholesale markets topazi began his career with alabama power in  as a cooperative education student engineer he held a number of positions at alabama power including western division vice president and birmingham division vice president while at the western division he served as chairman of the tuscaloosa county industrial development authority and had a primary role in recruiting the first mercedes benz automotive assembly plant outside of germany to the state of alabama topazi is chairman of momentum mississippi a publicprivate partnership appointed by the governor to enhance the states economic development future he previously served on the steering committee of blueprint mississippi and cochaired its economic development work group he serves as chairman of the gulf coast business council topazi is a member of the mississippi economic councils board of directors and vice chairman of the mississippi partnership for economic development topazi is a member of the united way detocqueville society and serves on the board of directors for the gulf coast community foundation he also serves on the board of directors for hancock bank infinity science center mississippi gulf coast chamber of commerce and on the board of trustees for the nature conservancy of mississippi topazi previously served as vice chairman of the governors commission on recovery rebuilding and renewal a birmingham native topazi earned a bachelor of science degree in electrical engineering from auburn university and also completed the advanced management program at harvard university he is a member of the engineering council at auburn university   anthony topazi colleagues  name title email tommy dulaney board dir please login aubrey patterson board dir please login philip terrell board dir please login frances turnage vp treasurer cfo please login kimberly flowers vp  generation sr production officer please login             home    about us    product information     subscription    list builder     executive list     email lists     contact us    site map    browse directory      �  walkerss research  a publisher of business information since  all rights reserved server error error unable to complete your request direct to the previous page the server encounted an internal error or misconfiguration and was unable to complete your requestplease contact the server administrator webmasterdfnpluscom and inform them of the time the error occured and anything you might have done that may have caused the error copyright  directfn ltd all rights reserved node contact us hello please use the below form for product support  feedback name   email  phone number   preferred contact method  email phone technical support x     slhopsdirectfnnet your account manager is   support  feedback anthony topazi  mississippi power company  zoominfocom insider trading  topazi anthony j  form  sec filings home  archives  products  about  contact  faq  new user sign up  sign in form  filings insider buys significant buys penny stocksinsider buying insider sales insider buy sell ratios stock options insider tradingstock screener insider tradinggraph view insider watch sec filings insider trading  topazi anthony j select time period  month  months  months  months  year  years  years  years all data       goo